OL,3,CFire in bin shed spreads to commercial
OL,4,Cpremises
OL,6,FAround 60 firefighters were called to
OL,7,Fa commercial premises in Maidstone
OL,8,Fwhen a fire broke out in a bin shed.
OL,10,FThe alarm was raised on Bircholt Road
OL,11,Fat 4:30pm (11 April) with anyone
OL,12,Fliving nearby urged to keep windows
OL,13,Fand doors closed.
OL,15,FSix fire engines were on site but the
OL,16,Foperation was scaled back in just over
OL,17,Fan hour with Kent Fire and Rescue
OL,18,FService saying it had made good
OL,19,Fprogress.
